{
  "stem": "15768.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She always wanted to teach nursery school children arts and crafts, and she had taken job in a shower curtain factory or shop, whatever-- however you want to call it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was painting designs on plastic shower curtains.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, lovely, big, free things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was left at home to do the housework, because in truth, she was tired.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was over-- well, she was 45 years old, 48 years old, and working all day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She came home-- Her relationship with her mother was not very good, and so I was sort of plunked right in the middle.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I shopped for my grandparents and did as much housework as I could.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so that was my responsibility, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my father, in the meantime, the younger brother who was sent to this country to open up a branch of the textile company, which my maternal grandfather was also in that business.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that is how my mother and father had initially met, that the two bosses had a meeting, and there was my mother as a young girl, and she was introduced to my father.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so, this younger brother of my mother's, who had come in 1932, had established a firm, a textile firm.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And recognizing that my father was very knowledgeable, that this had been his business, his factory, and he had contacts in Belgium and in France, took him into the business to manage.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "A lot of it was physical work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He-- he had some very strong and stout black workers loading trucks and things, and here was my-- my skinny, little father pushing these people around and directing things.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But he was very happy working for my uncle.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
